parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rear Light Bar Failure due to Water Ingress
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear light bar can cause a significant safety risk, as it can lead to rear-end collisions, especially at night or in low-visibility conditions. The failure can also result in police stops and fines.
symptoms: The rear light bar is not illuminated
water accumulation in the light bar
and the license plate light not functioning.
